<TR><TH>uhmm...<BR>
<I><FONT SIZE=-1>Posted 2000-04-10 19:49:48 by Aishen Nembrethil Ranger Priss o' Emarr</FONT></I></TH></TR>
<TR><TD>i'd be careful with AoE's....it might tickle something nearby that'll be conning neon red and slaughter you.  <BR><BR>
<BR><BR>
I only really use AoE's in emergency situations (i.e. a big train and there's 4 monsters on my caster and i need to pull them onto me...i'd pull invoke lightening because one shot will nuke all of them).<BR><BR>
<BR><BR>
just be really really careful when you cast the AoE.  make sure you look around to see there's nothing around the mob you're casting on that you wouldn't mind running after you.</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
